title: Mega trance compilation 12Hrs non stop
description:
This is a mp3 music file filled with over 12 hours of vocal trance and some dance, made to fit on a 700MB CD. Made it from some of the best tracks that I had at that time. I found this file a few days ago on an old hard drive. 


Time of creation: mid 2004
Duration: 12Hrs 38Min
Bitrate: 128
Sample rate: 32kHz

I have to admit that this is not the best quality but it works.
